00:00:03,800 --> 00:00:05,000
It's here.
找到了 

2
00:00:06,275 --> 00:00:09,900
I wonder how long it'll take to find the rest of it.
这得多久才能把剩下的碎片全部收集起来

3
00:00:10,125 --> 00:00:12,525
Kagome, let's go!
戈微   走吧

4
00:00:12,530 --> 00:00:14,520
-Er...   -What!
-额   -干嘛

5
00:00:14,530 --> 00:00:16,520
You never said my name before.
这是你第一次喊我的名字

6
00:00:17,050 --> 00:00:18,825
Yeah, what of it?
是啊   那又怎么样

7
00:00:18,830 --> 00:00:21,750
It's just that I think you like me more now. That's all.
感觉你现在不是那么讨厌我了呢

8
00:00:22,425 --> 00:00:24,100
Don't get excited.
有什么好激动的

9
00:00:24,110 --> 00:00:26,750
I still think you are pretty useless.
我还是觉得你没什么用处

10
00:00:26,950 --> 00:00:30,825
Remind me next time not to save you.
下次遇到危险记得提醒我千万不要管你

11
00:00:31,450 --> 00:00:34,675
If it hurts so much, you should've said something.
疼的话你倒是说呀

12
00:00:35,425 --> 00:00:37,800
Leave me alone!
不用你管

